\fIDefault\fP: \fBwiredTiger\fP
.sp
\fBNOTE:\fP
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
Starting in version 4.2, MongoDB removes the deprecated MMAPv1 storage
engine.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Specifies the storage engine for the \fBmongod\fP database. Available
values include:
