.TE
.sp
To change the maximum size during runtime, use the
\fBwiredTigerMaxCacheOverflowSizeGB\fP parameter.
.sp
\fIAvailable starting in MongoDB 4.2.1 (and 4.0.12)\fP
.UNINDENT
