.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-kmipRotateMasterKey <boolean>
\fIDefault\fP: false
.sp
New in version 3.2.

.sp
If true, rotate the master key and re\-encrypt the internal
keystore.
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
.IP "Enterprise Feature"
.sp
Available in MongoDB Enterprise only.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
\fBSEE ALSO:\fP
